
### learn in the selection space
sp {chunk*in*selection*space	
   (state <s> ^name selection
   	      ^problemspace learning)
-->
   (force-learn <s>)
}

### turn-off chunking for lgsoar
sp {turn-off*chunking*lgsoar
   (state <s> ^problem-space lgsoar)
-->
   (dont-learn <s>)
}

### turn-off chunking for interpretation problem-space
sp {turn-off*chunking*lgsoar
   (state <s> ^problem-space message-interpretation)
-->
   (dont-learn <s>)
}

